CINEMATIC_ATTACK_WHEN_POSSIBLE.label: 不閃避（不斷攻擊）
CINEMATIC_ATTACK_WHEN_POSSIBLE.description: 不斷使用快速招式，直到能量足夠使用能量招式

QUICK_ATTACK_ONLY.label: 只使用快速招式
QUICK_ATTACK_ONLY.description: 儘可能快地使用快速招式！

DODGE_SPECIALS2.label: 閃躲能量招式
DODGE_SPECIALS2.description: 使用快速招式，直到閃躲對手的能量招式，才使用我方的能量招式。

DODGE_SPECIALS.label: 閃躲能量招式 (專家)
DODGE_SPECIALS.description: 盡快使用快速招式和能量招式，但可以閃躲對手的能量招式！

DODGE_ALL2.label: 閃躲所有攻擊
DODGE_ALL2.description: 使用快速招式並閃躲對手的招式，直到閃躲對手的能量招式，才使用我方的能量招式。

DODGE_ALL.label: 閃躲所有攻擊 (專家)
DODGE_ALL.description: 使用快速招式和能量招式，閃躲對手所有招式！

DODGE_WEAVE_CAUTIOUS.label: 迂迴閃躲
DODGE_WEAVE_CAUTIOUS.description: 使用攻擊模式策略，假定最壞情況下，每次攻擊之間可能發生1.5秒的延遲。這個策略重現人為操作。

undefined.label: 未知
undefined.description: 這不應該出現，如果出現了請讓我們知道！

DODGE_100.label: 完美閃躲
DODGE_100.description: 試圖閃躲100％的攻擊。這個閃躲策略幾乎不會閃避失誤。您可能會遇到某些不可避免的情況，例如使用能量招式時

DODGE_REACTION_TIME.label: 真實閃躲
DODGE_REACTION_TIME.description: 嘗試模擬一個真實的人類躲避者。從50%(1秒反應時間的快速攻擊)到90%(3.5秒反應時間的慢速攻擊)不等的閃躲成功率。此外，如果攻擊者使用非常有效/不有效的攻擊，則還有另外25%的閃躲懲罰，將成功率降至37.5%至67.5%。

DODGE_REACTION_TIME2.label: 真實閃躲 (專家)
DODGE_REACTION_TIME2.description: 嘗試模擬一個真實的經驗豐富的人類躲避者。從70%(1秒反應時間的快速攻擊)到90%(3.5秒反應時間的慢速攻擊)不等的閃躲成功率。此外，如果攻擊者使用非常有效/不有效的攻擊，則還有另外10%的閃躲懲罰，將成功率降至63.0%至81.0%。最後，添加了微幅獎勵於較快速的攻擊招式，與閃躲動作相比速度越快，獎勵越多

DEFENSE.label: 預期防禦方
DEFENSE.description: 有效的預期統計結果。每2秒攻擊一次，能量攻擊總是在能量足夠後隔一次攻擊使用。

DEFENSE_LUCKY.label: 幸運防禦方
DEFENSE_LUCKY.description: 最差的戰鬥結果，每1.95秒攻擊一次，能量招式也是儘可能地提早

DEFENSE_RANDOM.label: 隨機
DEFENSE_RANDOM.description: 全隨機模擬！每1.5秒至2.5秒攻擊一次。如果能量足夠，每次攻擊使用能量招式的機會為50%。

DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC.label: 蒙地卡羅 - 金
DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC.description: 最準確的結果。執行100次隨機模擬並對其進行平均，以得到一個整體結果。戰鬥日誌實例採用基於整體評分的中位數結果。與非完美的閃避策略是最有用的組合

DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC_FAST.label: 蒙地卡羅 - 銅
DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC_FAST.description: A more accurate result. 10 random simulations are run and averaged together to make one overall result. The median result based on overall rating is used for combat logs as an example. Most useful in combination with non-perfect dodge strategies.

DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC_MID.label: 蒙地卡羅 - 銀
DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC_MID.description: A highly accurate result. 50 random simulations are run and averaged together to make one overall result. The median result based on overall rating is used for combat logs as an example. Most useful in combination with non-perfect dodge strategies.

DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC_EX.label: 蒙地卡羅 - 白金
DEFENSE_RANDOM_MC_EX.description: A special benefit for Fanatics and Champions. An excessively accurate result. 500 random simulations are run and combined together to make one overall result based on your aggregation choice. Most useful when looking at percentiles

DEFENSE_PATTERN.label: Defense Pattern - RNG
DEFENSE_PATTERN.description: An extremely predictable random number generator is used for this single simulation. This is used internally by Pokebattler for optimizing Monte Carlo simulations with random dodging

DEFENSE_PATTERN2.label: Defense Pattern
DEFENSE_PATTERN2.description: A pattern of delays and attacks is used for this single simulation. This is used internally by Pokebattler for optimizing Monte-Carlo simulations without dodging

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_UNSET.label: 非朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_UNSET.description: If you are not friends with anyone else in the raid, you get no bonus to attack.

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_0.label: 新朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_0.description: If you are new friends with anyone else in the raid, you get no bonus to attack. You can only trade regular Pokemon both players already own.

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_1.label: 好朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_1.description: The maximum friend level you have with anyone at the raid. Good Friends get a 3% bonus to attack and can trade non-mythical Pokemon.

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_2.label: 給力好朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_2.description: The maximum friend level you have with anyone at the raid. Great Friends get a 5% bonus to attack, 1 extra bonus ball in raids. They can trade non-mythical Pokemon with a 20% stardust discount.

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_3.label: 麻吉好朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_3.description: The maximum friend level you have with anyone at the raid. Ultra Friends get a 7% bonus to attack, 2 extra bonus balls in raids. They can trade non-mythical Pokemon with a 92% stardust discount.

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_4.label: 正港好朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_4.description: The maximum friend level you have with anyone at the raid. Best Friends get a 10% bonus to attack and 4 extra bonus balls in raids. They can trade non-mythical Pokemon with a 96% stardust discount.

FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_5.label: 永远的好朋友
FRIENDSHIP_LEVEL_5.description: 你在此团战中的最高朋友等级。永远的好朋友可获攻击 +12% 加成，并可进行远程交换。
